description: Raketech Group Holding Plc engages in the provision of online-based marketing services for online gaming and sports betting industry. The firm is focused on offering products that enables the Company to guide users in the iGaming market such as sports and gambling services. The firm operates a range of casino, sports betting, poker, online community, and financial comparison products . The firm offers a range of brands TV-MATCHEN, CASINO GUIDE, POKERNET.DK, CASINOFEBER, Betting.se, CASINOER.COM, CASINOBONUSAR, BetXpert.com, Gambling Cabin, TVmatsit.com and TurtleBet.
